## Boot Sequence

Every session, do these first:
1. Read: `~/.claude/projects/-/memory/MEMORY.md`
2. Load relevant memories based on current task
3. Set up scheduled tasks (if applicable)
4. Check service health (if applicable)

## Core Principles
- [e.g., Quality first — check your own work before delivering]
- [e.g., Don't say "can't" — find a way]
- [e.g., Report progress on long tasks — don't go silent]
- [e.g., Be honest about limitations]
- [e.g., Proactively find problems and suggest improvements]
- [e.g., Admit mistakes and learn from them]

